{"tid":700294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八男稱「可載回家」　20歲少女遭綁起輪姦","createTime":"2018-06-13T08:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T09:52:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":184,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":94,"replies":[{"pid":"49ea88e467d20db54bdfd1fe8c163de10d1f3207","tid":700294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:38:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180613/s00005/1528871353160\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180613%2Fs00005%2F1528871353160&d=HAZdIaBCQoHtnCf8pRKwwMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=29e93fc5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180613%2Fs00005%2F1528871353160&h=f7db5a66\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180613/s00005/1528871353160</a><br />\n<br />\n日本富山縣發生輪姦案。一名年約20歲的女子，在街上遭8名男子搭訕，稱可載她回家，卻將她帶到公寓輪流性侵。警方已將8名疑犯拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發在周日（10日）晚上6時至8時，日本富山縣一名20歲女子獨自走在路上，被8名25歲到31歲的男子搭訕，訛稱可開車載她回家。豈料8人將女子帶到公寓後態度突變，將其手腳綁起，輪流性侵約兩小時。其後女子趁機逃走並報警，警方在周一（11日）在公寓附近將8名疑犯拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n8名嫌犯分別為村中圭介（31歲）、堀下峻（30歲）、鄉倉郁也（30歲）、上谷知也（30歲）、松本浩之（30歲）、後田知之（30歲）、土林礼征（27歲），及端保貴大（25歲）。有部分人承認罪行，但有人辯稱事主屬自願性交。據了解，8名疑犯為同事及同學關係。<br />\n<br />\n（綜合報道）"},{"pid":"c67cfdfb6a93ae4c4e244c3cfa5355133743f100","tid":700294,"uid":34562,"like":576,"dislike":4,"score":572,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:41:15.000Z","msg":"估錯地方，係咪睇得太多h漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c62bc0c67c0b17534ba2ebe0812adf430a40868d","tid":700294,"uid":51932,"like":201,"dislike":1,"score":200,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:41:53.000Z","msg":"咁多30歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b462230886830508d50beb395cf346936337d4","tid":700294,"uid":162539,"like":136,"dislike":11,"score":125,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T08:42:25.000Z","msg":"地獄